hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Where's the postbox? erectafil side effects I don’t particularly like Weiner but his opponent clearly dug up all this dirt to help discredit this nutjob and this is a glaring admission on her part that she has very little to contribute, suffers from shakey morals and ethics, and has adopted a disturbing practice she’ll pursue and actively practice in the future against any and all perceived opposition. I don’t want someone like that as mayor just as much as I wouldn’t want a sexual predator like Weiner either.
